edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.schedule

Class Schedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.user.schedule.Schedule

  • public class Schedule
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a schedule, which contains an ArrayList of courses and a title. Allows users to manage their course schedule.
    Author:
    Matthew Strickland, William Boyles, Joey Davidson
